resources.string:
Upgrade method：
1.Place update.zip in the sdcard root directory and click the update button to upgrade。
2.Insert the USB flash drive and ensure that the update.zip file exists under the USB flash drive and a pop-up window will pop up to confirm the upgrade.
3.Send broadcast for upgrade
 Intent intent=new Intent("android.intent.action.FS_OTA_UPDATE");
 intent.putExtra("otaPath","/sdcard/update.zip");
 sendBroadcast(intent);
